Title: Aico 600 smoke alarm with 10 year lithium battery
Description: Less likely to react to cooking smells than other alarms, the Aico 600 Ei650RF RadioLINK+ battery optical smoke alarm is ideal for detecting slow, smouldering fires, as often produced by electrical fires or sofas. Containing a sealed-in, tamper-proof lithium battery that will last the full 10 year life of the device, this alarm won't receive power until twisted onto the mounting base, eliminating the issue of battery power consumption during storage. This alarm contains RadioLINK+ wireless interconnection technology, using radio frequency signals to link alarms together for additional functionality. All RadioLINK+ alarms and devices should be house-coded together upon install.
